working on tags and the ansible vault

tags: these are used to run a specific task or part of task which are inside the playbook
commands:
---------
1) ansible all -m ping --tags dev
2) 1) ansible all -m ping --tags 'dev,stage'
3) ansible all -m ping --list-tags
4) ansible all -m ping --skip-tags dev
5) ansible all -m ping --skip-tags 'dev,stage'